    <div class="banner">
        <h2 id="talk" >유치원·어린이집 등록</h2> 
        <h5 id="banner" >유치원·어린이집을 키즈가든에 등록할 수 있습니다.</h5>
    </div>
  <div class="wrapper row3">
    <main class="hoc container clear">              
      <div id="updatemento">          
        <form action="/register" method="post" id = "">
          <fieldset>
            <label for="username">유형</label>              
            <br><br>
            <label><input type="radio" name="type" value = "유치원" class = "radio">유치원</label>                                    
            <label class = "rightitem"><input type="radio" name="type"value = "어린이집" class = "radio">어린이집</label> 
            
          </fieldset>          
          <fieldset id = "margin">
            <label for="gender">기관명</label>              
            <button id = "addressBtn">주소찾기</button>
            <input type="text" id="address" name="firm" value = "" disabled>
            <input type="text" id="gardenname" name="firm" value = "" placeholder = "기관명" disabled>              
            </select>
          </fieldset>
          <fieldset>
            <label for="firm">작성자</label>              
            <input type="text" id="firm" name="firm" value = "">              
          </fieldset>
          <fieldset>
            <label for="department">원장명</label>
            <input type="text" id="department" name="department" value = "">
          </fieldset>
          <fieldset>
            <label for="career">주요경력</label>
            <textarea name="career" id="career" cols="30" rows="10"></textarea>
          </fieldset> 
          <fieldset>
            <label for="phone">휴대전화 번호</label>
            <input type="text" id="phone" name="phone" value = "">
          </fieldset>
          <fieldset>
            <label for="email">이메일</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" value = "" readonly >
          </fieldset>
          <fieldset>
            <label for="intro">멘토 소개</label>              
            <textarea name="intro" id="intro" cols="30" rows="10"></textarea>
            </fieldset>
          <fieldset>                       
          <fieldset>              
            <label for="name">프로필 사진</label>
            <label for="image" id = "upload">업로드</label>              
            <input type="file" value="업로드" name = "image" id = "image" accept="image/png, image/jpeg">
            <img id="image_section" src="" alt=""/>
            <div id="imagebox">
              <p>
                - 얼굴이 포함된 사진을 등록해주세요. <br>
                - 얼굴 확인이 어려울 경우, 수정 요청이 있을 수 있습니다. <br>
                - 해당 사진의 최적 사이즈는 800 x 800px 입니다. <br>
                - 등록 가능한 파일 형식은 jpg, png 입니다.
              </p>
            </div>
          </fieldset>            
          <input type="submit" value="다음" id = "mentor_submit">
        </form>
      </div>
